<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vszI0Qm3pDE/WJjC9FXYkMI/AAAAAAAALmg/N55BnZY2HVgYqfhNks8dUBZbk6yq5eiEACLcB/s1600/AP2060008.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="448" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vszI0Qm3pDE/WJjC9FXYkMI/AAAAAAAALmg/N55BnZY2HVgYqfhNks8dUBZbk6yq5eiEACLcB/s640/AP2060008.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-NYVrKW0280A/WJjC-IHUM1I/AAAAAAAALmk/iEum_0BKacsPh1tAqyBVaryHut4liKRgQCLcB/s1600/AP2060016.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="410" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-NYVrKW0280A/WJjC-IHUM1I/AAAAAAAALmk/iEum_0BKacsPh1tAqyBVaryHut4liKRgQCLcB/s640/AP2060016.jpg" width="640" /></a></div>Quite predictably the Nevis Range Gondola wasn't running in today's high winds which necessitated plan B for the first day of the <a href="http://www.expeditionguide.com/winterskills.php">Winter Skills Week</a>. Chris, Alan, David, John, Gerry and myself went instead to Glencoe and up to the closest bit of snow to the road that I could think of. Coire na Tulaich on Buachaille Etive Mor also gave reasonable shelter from the gale. As suspected there wasn't a firm enough base of older snow to run through any of the ice axe arrest scenarios but we made good use of the teaching opportunities that were present. Digging about on an objectively safe 30 degree slope gave great illustration of instability in a snow-pack. Our rutschblock failed immediately on loading and the hand shear for the most part slid with a light touch. These were weaknesses within the recently fallen snow (since Friday night) and there are weak bonds between a number of layers at varying depths. The wind is forecast to drop by tomorrow allowing us to get out onto the tops. We'll have to be careful in our choice of route to take though.<br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ktTsXdvbQmQ/WJjC-7Um9jI/AAAAAAAALmo/JC2MG5pbnL4Kp9dihy90cqi1CHSBsdZjACLcB/s1600/AP2060020.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="444" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-ktTsXdvbQmQ/WJjC-7Um9jI/AAAAAAAALmo/JC2MG5pbnL4Kp9dihy90cqi1CHSBsdZjACLcB/s640/AP2060020.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-EvXs9qeUXZw/WJjC_eRLTzI/AAAAAAAALms/axHxC-D4CicBUHPr2QF6cQdbPbLXtSTJACLcB/s1600/AP2060027.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="400" src="https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-EvXs9qeUXZw/WJjC_eRLTzI/AAAAAAAALms/axHxC-D4CicBUHPr2QF6cQdbPbLXtSTJACLcB/s640/AP2060027.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-urFLN6ZG44E/WJjDAbdsXmI/AAAAAAAALmw/mN2LKItmK3kikcOXxR6z_bEU8WoN1R4NACLcB/s1600/AP2060034.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="422" src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-urFLN6ZG44E/WJjDAbdsXmI/AAAAAAAALmw/mN2LKItmK3kikcOXxR6z_bEU8WoN1R4NACLcB/s640/AP2060034.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2fVSvaA8egs/WJjDBPySylI/AAAAAAAALm0/N8Sh4-PDAQQFn-MYID2BK5oPEW5ZHlO7QCLcB/s1600/AP2060040.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" height="442" src="https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2fVSvaA8egs/WJjDBPySylI/AAAAAAAALm0/N8Sh4-PDAQQFn-MYID2BK5oPEW5ZHlO7QCLcB/s640/AP2060040.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br />